quid chlorine, hydrogen gas, hydrochloric acid, and sodium hypochlorite/bleach liquor products; sodium chlorate; and alkali, acids, bases, solvents, alcohols, gases, ethers, aliphatics, aromatics, aldehydes ketones, amines, alkaloids, potassium chlorate, perchlorate, and other chemicals, as well as its by-products and derivatives. It also provides industrial grade and edible salt products; and PVCO pipes. The company was formerly known as Teamec Chlorates Limited and changed its name to Chemfab Alkalis Limited in July 2017. Chemfab Alkalis Limited was founded in 1985 and is based in Chennai, India."}}